<P>__{(snaps)}
<D>__{no you're not}
<P>__{(off his look)}
<D>__{you're glad, because now you've got a witness.}
<P>__{(and)}
<D>__{i heard the other police talking last night.}
<P>__{(and)}
<D>__{they don't seem to like you very much.}
